    "type": "comment",
    "z": "c3_tab_main",
    "name": "4) ZBEE_ZCL: publish to ZigBee/<device>, queue rate limit 10/min, then filtered_elems + charts",
    "info": "Topic must be ZigBee/<Device Name ZigBee Source>. Delay node must queue, not drop.",
